_sText:
Castle_base_b2 is a bomb/defuse tactical map. CT's spawn on one side of the maze and the T's on the other. T's can choose to plant the bomb in the sewer tunnels or around the Ct spawn area.

Watch Out! If you break one of the structures legs, its coming down!

PLEASE READ THE INSTALLTION.TXT FILE BEFORE PLAYING!

Map created by Duck of Source Development Team
Custom Source Development team texture created by Culda of Source Development Team

http://halomoddingsite.com/meteoraCSS/index.php
